
Amazon RDS Proxy

What is RDS Proxy?
A fully managed database proxy that improves application scalability and resiliency by pooling database connections.

Key Benefits:
Efficient connection management for high-throughput workloads.
Improved failover time for Aurora and RDS databases.
Secure with AWS IAM and Secrets Manager integration.

Example Use Case:
A web app with Lambda accessing an Aurora databaseâ€”RDS Proxy reduces the overhead of connection management.

